  "texts": [
    "During this loop, the process involves observing and retaining information using elastic memory and comprehending the learning material (Torabi et al., 2019).",
    "Figure 1 below illustrates how imitation (Liu et al., 2018; Tangkaratt et al., 2020) plays a significant role in paving the way for the subsequent t invention loop.",
    "Notably, when an unusual occurrence arises, it serves as a trigger for the recreation process.",
    "The creation of a habit loop involves the cultivation of specific listening and speaking that build upon learners' existing behaviours.",
    "Integrating these behaviours into instructional objectives is key to enhancing learning achievement."
  ]
}